statements.sql:
select `bravo_locations`.*, `bravo_locations`.`name` as `title` from `bravo_locations` where `bravo_locations`.`status` = 'publish' and (`bravo_locations`.`airport_code` like '%Lko%' or `bravo_locations`.`name` like '%Lko%' or `bravo_locations`.`airport_name` like '%Lko%') and `bravo_locations`.`deleted_at` is null order by CASE
WHEN airport_code LIKE '%Lko%' THEN 1
WHEN name LIKE '%Lko%' THEN 2
WHEN airport_name LIKE '%Lko%' THEN 3
ELSE 4
END, `airport_code` asc limit 20
